The '''''American Journal of Applied Sciences''''' is a monthly [[peer-reviewed]] [[open access]] [[academic journal]] publishing original research articles in the fields of [[chemistry]], [[business]] and [[economics]], [[physics]], [[geology]], [[engineering]], [[mathematics]], [[statistics]], and [[computer science]]. The journal was established in 2004 and is published by [[Science Publications]].

The journal is abstracted and indexed in [[Scopus]] and [[Inspec]].

